cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.IR, cs.AI. 

The paper focuses on developing an automatic diagnostic system using textual admission information from Electronic Health Records (EHRs) and proposes a Convolutional Neural Network model for predicting primary discharge diagnosis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, specifically deep learning, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper deals with medical data and healthcare, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the use of neural networks for diagnosis prediction falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
